ld (Val'Kori) in fear =( ok ill ask politely if golem is up and if they are going after him. Nope there not and as soon as they are done im free to bring in my force to kill him, thanks Val'Kori =). Now its 1 am not many in guild are left, and Val'kori is done. So i start asking around if anyone is free to help. Doesn't look good, only one group so far. I ask an allied guild member and he says sure no prob ill get a few together for ya, bam he shows up with 3 full groups, with the perfect classes for doing golem big thanks to Black Tower. Everything was flawless on killing him I looted oil and procedded to /dance.<br> <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/ualejandrodigraip.showPublicProfile?language=EN>alejandro digraip</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(1/31/02 12:02:22 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm5.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1864.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Got my Epic =)</span><hr size=1> Congratulations man.  I wish I had your fortune.  Phinny has not been kind to me and I have set my mind to getting his staff before VS.  Those are the 2 remaining that I need, so if anyone on Mith Marr wants to help out a frustrated wizzy get a piece of his epic, I would be most appreciative.<br><br> <p><a href=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=74497>Alejandro DiGraip 55 Wizard</a></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uyvil.showPublicProfile?language=EN>yvil</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(2/1/02 11:44:06 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm5.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1864.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Got my Epic =)</span><hr size=1> Dont wait, if you can get VS get him.  MQ'ing is so fraught with risk and it really cheapens it.  You need to have absolute faith in the other guy to not waste the piece.<br><br>You might kill VS more than phinny, and hes a lot harder to get to.  More guild interest typically and more competition.  So dont try to do the mobs in order, just kill them all and sort it out later. <p><div align="center"><img src="http://www.3drealm.net/webshare/sigs/yvil-sig.gif"></img><br><img src="http://www.3drealm.net/webshare/sigs/naggykill.gif"></img></div></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/ueccezanfyresky.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Eccezan Fyresky</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Channeler</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(2/2/02 11:10:14 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm5.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1864.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Got my Epic =)</span><hr size=1> 0/5 on phinny, last kill was last night...it really makes me frustrated...<br><br>always drops infused coral <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :( --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/frown.gif ALT=":("><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br><br>and <br><br>staff of the trident -- crap <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :( --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/frown.gif ALT=":("><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br><br><br>Eccezan Fyresky<br>60 - High Elf Sorcerer <br>Fennin Ro  <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm5.showPrevMessage?topicID=1864.topic"> << Prev Topic</